Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Bush's 1989 speech at the United Nations
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydt74
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 29 Sep 1989
President Bush's 1989 speech at the United Nations, the sleeping menace of nuclear weapons and the president's unusually high popularity in his early days in office.